ds have ranged 20–120 % APY). MetaMask added direct Polymarket access on Decembe
r 4, 2025. Growth is projected into 2026, though regulatory restrictions, manipu
lation incidents, and high retail loss rates (85–90 %) are documented concerns.\
n\nPrediction markets are platforms that facilitate trading of contracts based o
n the outcomes of future events, such as Bitcoin price levels, Federal Reserve r
ate decisions, or Super Bowl results. In 2025, these markets have experienced no
table expansion, with cumulative trading volume across major platforms exceeding
