zed exchange on Polygon and Solana, and Kalshi, a CFTC-regulated platform primar
ily serving U.S. users.\n\nThis guide examines prediction markets in 2025, inclu
ding a step-by-step explanation of how Kalshi operates, the CNN partnership with
