ny fees you might incur:\n\n-  fees = round up(0.07 x C x P x (1-P))\n\n-  P = t
he price of a contract in dollars (50 cents is 0.5)\n\n-  C = the number of cont
racts being traded\n\n-  round up = rounds to the next cent\n\n#### Can I Trade 
