key | Set env var or run `sample_data_loader.py` |\n| `feature_names mismatch` |
Model trained with different columns | Ensure `data_bridge.py` produces all expe
cted columns |\n| `No trained models found` | Ivan hasn\'t trained models yet | 
Run `../../ivan/models/nfp_nowcast/train.py` |\n| Empty predictions | All featur
es are NaN | Check that `sample_data_loader.py` generated enough history (≥36 mo
nths) |\n| No signals generated | Model probabilities align with market prices |
Normal — only trade when edge > 5% |\n\n---\n\n## Next Steps / TODO\n\n1. **Bob:
** Confirm actual Kalshi ticker format for NFP threshold markets.\n2. **Bob:** P
rovide live API endpoint for fetching NFP market prices.\n3. **Dave:** Confirm s
ignal format is accepted by `StrategyRunner` without transformation.\n4. **Ivan:
